*[[Mus<U+00E9>e Jacquemart-Andr<U+00E9>]] &mdash; private collection from the renaissance to the nineteenth century
*[http://www.fondation.cartier.fr/ Fondation Cartier] &mdash; contemporary Art
*[[Centre National de la photographie]]
*[http://www.bourdelle.paris.fr Mus<U+00E9>e Bourdelle] &mdash; the sculptor [[Emile-Antoine Bourdelle]]
*[http://www.dapper.fr.com Mus<U+00E9>e Dapper] &mdash; African art
*[http://www.musee-moreau.fr Mus<U+00E9>e Gustave Moreau] &mdash; the symbolist painter [[Gustave Moreau]]
*[[Manufacture des Gobelins]] &mdash; tapestries and weaving from the 17th century
*[http://www.lesartsdecoratifs.fr/fr/04museecamondo/index.html Mus<U+00E9>e Nissim de Camondo] &mdash; private collection of 18th century works
*[http://www.museemaillol.com/ Mus<U+00E9>e Maillol] &mdash; Fondation Dina Vierny &mdash; the sculptor [[Aristide Maillol]]
*[http://www.mep-fr.org/ Maison Europ<U+00E9>enne de la Photographie]
*[http://www.musee-ceramique-sevres.fr/ Mus<U+00E9>e de C<U+00E9>ramique <U+00E0> S<U+00E8>vres]
*[[Mus<U+00E9>e du Montparnasse]]

