==Vocabulary==
French words and expressions dealing with the arts:
*''peinture'' &mdash; painting, paint
**''peinture <U+00E0> l'huile'' &mdash; [[oil painting]]
*''tableau'' &mdash; painting
*''toile'' &mdash; canvas
*''gravure'' &mdash; [[engraving]]
*''dessin'' &mdash; drawing
*''aquarelle'' &mdash; [[watercolor]]
*''croquis'' &mdash; sketch
*''<U+00E9>bauche'' &mdash; study
*''crayon'' &mdash; pencil, a pencil drawing
*''paysage'' &mdash; [[Landscape art|landscape]]
*''nature morte'' &mdash; [[still life]]
*''la peinture d'histoire'' &mdash; [[History painting]], see [[Hierarchy of genres]]

